{"tid":2374332,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"陳偉霆瞪大雙眼挑影后機，網民:他不紅誰該紅！！！","createTime":"2021-01-21T07:04:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-22T13:03:13.000Z","uid":20032,"like":4,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"30a1ad6383e9b66c7eed2196f738a31cd1592990","tid":2374332,"uid":20032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T07:04:19.000Z","msg":"藝人陳偉霆（William）於大陸發展得有聲有色，歌影視三方面都非常出色！喺即將上映嘅電影《侍神令》中挑戰做反派，以一頭紅髮上陣飾演陰陽師，邪氣逼人！雖然戲未有得睇，不過可以一睹William同影后周迅嘅對戲花絮止住癮先！<br />\n<br />\n周迅要拍攝被William掐頸嘅戲份，工作人員在旁幫手一直收緊繩子，而周迅臉色開始變化，一面痛苦，更誇張得青筋暴現、滿面通紅，而William就瞪大雙眼，眼神凌厲非常嚇人！導演嗌Cut後，周迅回一回氣就建議William說話動作慢啲，顯得比較壞！<br />\n<br />\n唔少網民都大讚周迅真係好好戲，而William演技再備受討論，有人留言：「陳偉霆演反派，非常可以！」、「雞皮疙瘩都起來了！」、「他不紅誰該紅！！！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LqCCW38.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLqCCW38.jpg&h=4b9b4405&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XK4UZht.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXK4UZht.jpg&h=64f99931&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iobXcCu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiobXcCu.jpg&h=61dd1a69&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4fn7zQQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4fn7zQQ.jpg&h=942e2841&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/08oZqXv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F08oZqXv.jpg&h=d9fb2d28&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7mcO3Kb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7mcO3Kb.jpg&h=85cbb07a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d8bcf479ebf46759411c3675fcbd14fd4ab073c3","tid":2374332,"uid":20032,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T07:04:43.000Z","msg":"逼不及待想看看了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"822c7761109ba9c7fdbca90590e2876948d93892","tid":2374332,"uid":128741,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,